  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2026-03-19 18:30</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e7521e00&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUibyxhuYSuFY8wwgEkzicffhjIaPQGpLF9ptDiaKFBicGlZ9ibglChCBmT4nbRicPnIib63bOxDuUoa5VgTlSdTjn24jboVgcriaUT4C0qLtOF3KdX8%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>紧凑的视觉语言模型家族Penguin-VL，机器人操作的合成数据生成引擎InternDataEngine，图像风格化项目EmoStyle，渐进物理对齐框架ProPhy，可扩展的、端到端可训练的稀疏潜在记忆框架MSA，流匹配策略A2A_Flow_Matching</p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Penguin-VL</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6435185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1030\" data-imgfileid=\"100018190\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f4cd9740&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZbVN9fzpvEtZxEpdvoicYLrwmzncicaRpaYrLR2DKiafONCsf8OZ0fbR3vuicRKtLr7tyXzL6S2a192hbjs5Kckbvuv7yaxF9LvR8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Penguin-VL是一个紧凑的视觉语言模型家族，旨在通过重新设计视觉编码器来研究多模态效率的极限，而不仅仅是扩大数据或模型规模。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与依赖于大规模对比目标预训练的现代视觉语言模型不同，Penguin-VL引入了从仅文本的大型语言模型初始化的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉编码器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，使视觉骨干更接近语言模型表示空间，从而更高效地学习数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/penguin-vl\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/penguin-vl</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：InternDataEngine</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5361111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"858\" data-imgfileid=\"100018193\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51735edb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZnAia8KgMtoBpWUpRMddGC27KMPRhfzGGftpFYXQTnZnmYdLzuUHiaTF41oseZ7srCibEibNmxibzRYe38e6wUh57x6AxNst6ZVsKA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★InternDataEngine是一个用于机器人操作的合成数据生成引擎，旨在支持大规模模型训练和迭代。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该引擎基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">NVIDIA Isaac Sim</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">构建，结合了InternData-A1的高保真物理交互、InternData-M1的语义任务和场景生成，以及Nimbus框架的高吞吐量调度，提供了真实、任务对齐且大规模可扩展的机器人操作数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/interndataengine\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/interndataengine</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：EmoStyle</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5685185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"910\" data-imgfileid=\"100018192\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51676f0d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZXH3DqddMxj97WbRAYaly5xnSPicWRZ6BXgtSjwtkCOSdibjXsoWOiaWYYXHuh5xCJib6FC9t2dsVmdVMY8InaSkfNVDLGpOsmw20%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★EmoStyle是一个情感驱动的图像风格化项目，旨在通过艺术风格化将用户提供的图像转换为特定的情感响应。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目不需要参考图像或详细的文本描述，只需</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">情感词</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为提示。EmoStyle通过引入情感-内容推理器和风格量化器，将连续查询映射到离散风格原型，生成具有真实情感和保留内容的风格化图像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/emostyle\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/emostyle</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：ProPhy</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4203703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"673\" data-imgfileid=\"100018191\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e00f6d74&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaycZxfwQ8HRvboKgO615OB8HJuGbfAiaYvGmJSLjsSJ5IrrEqnyicZxQdOpFXGVX3joHiaGkOz5SQ3Jsmibicx4KJFicmgzzDX9lcCc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ProPhy是一种用于动态世界模拟的渐进物理对齐框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与依赖隐式对齐或粗略视频级路由的先前工作相比，ProPhy引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">渐进对齐框架</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，注入可学习的物理先验，并采用细粒度的令牌级路由，使专门的专家能够内化特定的物理领域，提高生成视频的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">物理真实性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/prophy\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/prophy</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：MSA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48518518518518516\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"776\" data-imgfileid=\"100018189\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1d8e169&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYthM11wzzicerUwvicicFX7QFiaaYDZtVciasMOLs3UdQaSj9icrl4rqU8ciaT02v7p0OMpvXxjZLppNx3HqXk2ctIiaFYv1kSrQnMRuU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MSA（Memory Sparse Attention) 是一个可扩展的、端到端可训练的稀疏潜在记忆框架，旨在解决长上下文处理中的注意力瓶颈问题。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">MSA通过结合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可扩展的稀疏注意力和文档级RoPE</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，实现了在训练和推理中的近线性复杂度。该框架在长上下文问答和NIAH基准测试中表现优异，能够在16K到100M的上下文范围内保持小于9%的性能衰减，展示了将记忆容量与推理能力解耦的实际路径。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/msa\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/msa</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：A2A_Flow_Matching</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30648148148148147\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"490\" data-imgfileid=\"100018194\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c600f4f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZsOs2EM8gjjvNTquytGGE4vslAuQcmr62q8nUFXnAUpmH6rOzJYPKGEYcSSPqXQMrQnO7EB4F2PVIeeH1HM3M1iaBz2IdALERQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★A2A_Flow_Matching是一种流匹配策略，旨在通过视觉观察将历史动作分布直接转换为未来动作分布。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">RoboVerse</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">平台实现，主要用于机器人操作任务中的高效和鲁棒的模仿学习。A2A通过学习从历史状态到未来动作的转换，提升了机器人在复杂环境中的操作能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/a2a-flow-matching\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/a2a-flow-matching</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: center;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span style=\"padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.5712962962962962\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100012181\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=050dd75e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzsuveu0Oib7RPoas9iaReIDLd72zAJkrNOCp7A0IRgbeicADqBSicz36BLdGh2dz1C7E5PZgibCqFNSRQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.18518518518518517\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);letter-spacing: 0.578px;width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"100013546\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=73250edd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDky46ibiaDkwPpOl085OGW8JMM572LKqicN8ordMGb1lKKwclv8NbFEOlFRqAojINufXDNiaERbIkUv8EQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=51a5cdd6&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkyMzcwMDIyMQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247501847%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D805d1370a235ddfa747422b3924d6c19\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月 19 日的开源 AI 项目动态，重点介绍了 Penguin-VL、InternDataEngine、EmoStyle、ProPhy、MSA 及 A2A_Flow_Matching 等 6 个前沿模型与工具。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总了 2026 年 3 月 19 日的开源 AI 项目动态，重点介绍了 Penguin-VL、InternDataEngine、EmoStyle、ProPhy、MSA 及 A2A_Flow_Matching 等 6 个前沿模型与工具。",
  "summary": "该文章由「机器之心 SOTA 模型」发布，精选并简要介绍了当日值得关注的 6 个开源 AI 项目。内容涵盖了紧凑型视觉语言模型 Penguin-VL、机器人合成数据引擎 InternDataEngine、情感驱动图像风格化工具 EmoStyle、动态世界模拟框架 ProPhy、长上下文稀疏注意力框架 MSA，以及用于机器人模仿学习的流匹配策略 A2A_Flow_Matching。文章为开发者提供了快速了解前沿技术进展的窗口，并附带了项目直达链接，适合快速筛选感兴趣的技术方向。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Penguin-VL：通过重新设计视觉编码器提升效率",
      "explanation": "Penguin-VL 引入了从纯文本 LLM 初始化的视觉编码器，使视觉骨干更接近语言模型表示空间，从而在不依赖大规模对比预训练的情况下提升多模态效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "InternDataEngine：机器人操作的合成数据引擎",
      "explanation": "基于 NVIDIA Isaac Sim 构建，整合了高保真物理交互、语义任务生成和高吞吐量调度，为机器人大规模模型训练提供数据支持。"
    },
    {
      "point": "MSA (Memory Sparse Attention)：解决长上下文瓶颈",
      "explanation": "通过结合可扩展的稀疏注意力和文档级 RoPE，在 16K 到 100M 上下文范围内实现近线性复杂度，且性能衰减极小。"
    },
    {
      "point": "ProPhy：提升视频生成的物理真实性",
      "explanation": "引入渐进物理对齐框架，注入可学习的物理先验，并采用细粒度令牌级路由，使模型能内化特定的物理领域。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Penguin-VL 是一个紧凑的视觉语言模型家族，旨在通过重新设计视觉编码器来研究多模态效率的极限。",
    "MSA 通过结合可扩展的稀疏注意力和文档级 RoPE，实现了在训练和推理中的近线性复杂度。",
    "InternDataEngine 是一个用于机器人操作的合成数据生成引擎，旨在支持大规模模型训练和迭代。"
